# Debian OS-level CVEs with no upstream fix available.
# PaddleOCR requires glibc and cannot run on Alpine.
# These packages are transitive deps of the base image, not used by the application.
# Re-evaluate when Debian releases patches.

# mesa/libgbm1 — GPU rendering libs, OCR runs on CPU only
CVE-2026-40393

# libexpat — XML parser, transitive dep
CVE-2026-25210

# ncurses — terminal UI, not used in headless container
CVE-2025-69720

# nghttp2 — HTTP/2 lib, transitive dep of curl
CVE-2026-27135

# systemd/libudev — init system libs, not used in container
CVE-2026-29111
